data.description: Escape to the serene countryside with this charming and well-maintained manufactured home, now available for sale on a sprawling one-acre lot. This residence offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and the tranquility of country living. House has 30x40 addition (2 rooms), a 24x24 detached garage & large shed on one acre of land with panoramic views from the deck. Has area for wood burning stove. Selling as-is.
